+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                     Knowledge Graph Construction                           |
|                           (NetworkX / Neo4j)                               |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Nodes:                                                                      |
| - Papers                                                                    |
| - Datasets                                                                  |
| - Researchers                                                               |
| Relationships:                                                              |
| - Citations ('CITES')                                                       |
| - Authorship                                                                |
| - Data sharing                                                              |
| Metadata per node/edge:                                                     |
| - Abstract Embeddings                                                       |
| - Timestamp ('added_date')                                                  |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
            |                             |                          |
            v                             v                          v
+-------------------+    +------------------+    +-------------------------------+
| Structural Metrics|    | Semantic Metrics |    | Objective Knowledge Update    |
+-------------------+    +------------------+    +-------------------------------+
| - Connectivity    |    | - Similarity     |    | - Recent Nodes/Edges Rate     |
| - Degree Centrality|   | - Completeness   |    |   (based on timestamps)       |
| - PageRank        |    | - Coverage       |    | - Temporal update frequency   |
| - Betweenness     |    | - Diversity      |    |   (defined objectively by     |
| - Clustering Coef.|    |                  |    |   recent additions)           |
