+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                        Integrated Metrics Computation                             |
|                         (Weighted aggregation into S Index)                       |
|                                                                                   |
| S Index = (structural_weight * structural_score)                                  |
|          + (semantic_weight * semantic_score)                                     |
|          + (data_sharing_weight * data_sharing_score)                             |
|          + (knowledge_update_weight * knowledge_update_score)                     |
